{"id": "animal-brown-prinia-112", "type": "fact", "statement": "The Brown Prinia (Prinia polychroa) is a bird classified as Least Concern by conservation authorities.", "explanation": "Found primarily in various habitats worldwide, the Brown Prinia is a fascinating bird. Scientists classify it as Prinia polychroa. With a conservation status of Least Concern, this species maintains healthy populations.", "wowFactor": "This feathered wonder proves nature's creativity knows no bounds!", "quizQuestion": "Where can Brown Prinia primarily be found?", "correctAnswer": "various habitats worldwide", "distractors": [{"text": "European Alps", "difficultyTier": "easy"}, {"text": "African savanna", "difficultyTier": "easy"}, {"text": "Sahara Desert", "difficultyTier": "easy"}, {"text": "North American prairies", "difficultyTier": "medium"}, {"text": "Deep ocean trenches", "difficultyTier": "medium"}, {"text": "Australian outback", "difficultyTier": "medium"}, {"text": "Central American cloud forests", "difficultyTier": "hard"}, {"text": "Himalayan mountains", "difficultyTier": "hard"}], "variants": [{"question": "What animal group does Brown Prinia belong to?", "type": "forward", "correctAnswer": "Birds", "distractors": ["Crustacean", "Reptile", "Insect"]}, {"question": "What is the scientific name of Brown Prinia?", "type": "reverse", "correctAnswer": "Prinia polychroa", "distractors": ["Meles meles", "Salamandra salamandra", "Python reticulatus"]}, {"question": "Which is NOT true about Brown Prinia?", "type": "negative", "correctAnswer": "Critically Endangered", "distractors": ["Least Concern status", "Classified as bird", "Has a scientific name"]}, {"question": "The scientific name of Brown Prinia is ___.", "type": "fill_blank", "correctAnswer": "Prinia polychroa", "distractors": ["Lucanus cervus", "Balaenoptera musculus", "Passer domesticus"]}, {"question": "The Brown Prinia is classified as Least Concern.", "type": "true_false", "correctAnswer": "True", "distractors": ["Fal