{"id": "animal-murray-cod-113", "type": "fact", "statement": "Known scientifically as Maccullochella peelii, the Murray cod is a fish currently listed as Least Concern.", "explanation": "Maccullochella peelii, commonly known as the Murray cod, inhabits various habitats worldwide. This fish has been assessed as Least Concern by conservationists, meaning its populations remain relatively stable in the wild.", "wowFactor": "Few fish species display such remarkable adaptations!", "quizQuestion": "Which species is known as the Murray cod?", "correctAnswer": "Maccullochella peelii", "distractors": [{"text": "Bufo bufo", "difficultyTier": "easy"}, {"text": "Giraffa camelopardalis", "difficultyTier": "easy"}, {"text": "Crocodylus niloticus", "difficultyTier": "easy"}, {"text": "Chelonia mydas", "difficultyTier": "medium"}, {"text": "Danaus plexippus", "difficultyTier": "medium"}, {"text": "Passer domesticus", "difficultyTier": "medium"}, {"text": "Meles meles", "difficultyTier": "hard"}, {"text": "Salmo salar", "difficultyTier": "hard"}], "variants": [{"question": "What animal group does Murray cod belong to?", "type": "forward", "correctAnswer": "Fishs", "distractors": ["Amphibian", "Bird", "Mammal"]}, {"question": "What is the scientific name of Murray cod?", "type": "reverse", "correctAnswer": "Maccullochella peelii", "distractors": ["Felis catus", "Passer domesticus", "Elephas maximus"]}, {"question": "Which is NOT true about Murray cod?", "type": "negative", "correctAnswer": "Critically Endangered", "distractors": ["Least Concern status", "Classified as fish", "Has a scientific name"]}, {"question": "The scientific name of Murray cod is ___.", "type": "fill_blank", "correctAnswer": "Maccullochella peelii", "distractors": ["Crocodylus niloticus", "Thunnus thynnus", "Rana temporaria"]}, {"question": "The Murray cod is classified as Least Concern.", "type": "true_false", "correctAnswer": "True", "distractors": ["False"]}], "difficulty": 3, "funScore": 4, "visualDescriptio